{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/travel/2020/07/25/长沙博物馆还是值得去的.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"c4ae157a-1544-5479-bfa2-2f157a2c3f5c","excerpt":"…","html":"<h1>长沙市博物馆还是值得去的</h1>\n<p>之前我去<a href=\"/travel/2019/04/07/%E6%B9%98%E6%B1%9F%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E7%99%BE%E8%88%B8%E4%BA%89%E6%B5%81%E5%80%92%E6%9C%89%E6%B1%89%E5%A2%93%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7.html\">湖南省博物馆</a>看过马王堆女尸，本来及已经很震撼了，但是长沙其实还有一座值得去的博物馆，就是长沙博物馆。</p>\n<p>考虑到古时候的长沙是比整个湖南还要大一点的地方，而且长沙是一个历史可以追溯到战国时期，它在唐之前的历史是可以再单独布置一套博物馆用于展示的。长沙博物馆距离北辰三角洲地铁站还有大概一公里的距离。</p>\n<h2>看什么</h2>\n<p>长沙古时是楚国的属地，楚国的青铜器是一绝，确切的说，我国南方的青铜器都比北方要精致。就我个人看来，应该是北方产铜量比不上南方；铸造技术传到南方的时间比较晚，已经成熟；再加上北方更早进入铸铁阶段，技术更新太快导致艺术上就没那么高追求了。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9f3d980257b6e703c17258399c7a9d71/4b190/2020-07-25-0.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.37837837837838%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/9f3d980257b6e703c17258399c7a9d71/cbe2e/2020-07-25-0.webp 148w,\n/static/9f3d980257b6e703c17258399c7a9d71/3084c/2020-07-25-0.webp 295w,\n/static/9f3d980257b6e703c17258399c7a9d71/5ca24/2020-07-25-0.webp 590w,\n/static/9f3d980257b6e703c17258399c7a9d71/d00b9/2020-07-25-0.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/9f3d980257b6e703c17258399c7a9d71/a80bd/2020-07-25-0.jpg 148w,\n/static/9f3d980257b6e703c17258399c7a9d71/1c91a/2020-07-25-0.jpg 295w,\n/static/9f3d980257b6e703c17258399c7a9d71/1c72d/2020-07-25-0.jpg 590w,\n/static/9f3d980257b6e703c17258399c7a9d71/4b190/2020-07-25-0.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/9f3d980257b6e703c17258399c7a9d71/1c72d/2020-07-25-0.jpg\"\n          alt=\"青铜剑\"\n          title=\"青铜剑\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">青铜剑</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b47c1e8523d15413b45fc7c96da4f8a4/4b190/2020-07-25-2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 76.35135135135135%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/b47c1e8523d15413b45fc7c96da4f8a4/cbe2e/2020-07-25-2.webp 148w,\n/static/b47c1e8523d15413b45fc7c96da4f8a4/3084c/2020-07-25-2.webp 295w,\n/static/b47c1e8523d15413b45fc7c96da4f8a4/5ca24/2020-07-25-2.webp 590w,\n/static/b47c1e8523d15413b45fc7c96da4f8a4/d00b9/2020-07-25-2.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/b47c1e8523d15413b45fc7c96da4f8a4/a80bd/2020-07-25-2.jpg 148w,\n/static/b47c1e8523d15413b45fc7c96da4f8a4/1c91a/2020-07-25-2.jpg 295w,\n/static/b47c1e8523d15413b45fc7c96da4f8a4/1c72d/2020-07-25-2.jpg 590w,\n/static/b47c1e8523d15413b45fc7c96da4f8a4/4b190/2020-07-25-2.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/b47c1e8523d15413b45fc7c96da4f8a4/1c72d/2020-07-25-2.jpg\"\n          alt=\"青铜铙\"\n          title=\"青铜铙\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">青铜铙</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>另一个，因为长沙国作为封国的时间比较久（到了东汉时期依然存在），大量的墓葬都按照汉国王室墓制处理而又没有过度盗掘，保留了很多诸如黄肠题凑、金缕玉衣的墓葬制度，可以一饱眼福。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e4839b79ae89287f738cbf73596122dd/4b190/2020-07-25-3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.89189189189189%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/e4839b79ae89287f738cbf73596122dd/cbe2e/2020-07-25-3.webp 148w,\n/static/e4839b79ae89287f738cbf73596122dd/3084c/2020-07-25-3.webp 295w,\n/static/e4839b79ae89287f738cbf73596122dd/5ca24/2020-07-25-3.webp 590w,\n/static/e4839b79ae89287f738cbf73596122dd/d00b9/2020-07-25-3.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/e4839b79ae89287f738cbf73596122dd/a80bd/2020-07-25-3.jpg 148w,\n/static/e4839b79ae89287f738cbf73596122dd/1c91a/2020-07-25-3.jpg 295w,\n/static/e4839b79ae89287f738cbf73596122dd/1c72d/2020-07-25-3.jpg 590w,\n/static/e4839b79ae89287f738cbf73596122dd/4b190/2020-07-25-3.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/e4839b79ae89287f738cbf73596122dd/1c72d/2020-07-25-3.jpg\"\n          alt=\"黄肠题凑\"\n          title=\"黄肠题凑\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">黄肠题凑</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>再一个，在近代馆里面看见了「万国图志」的原本。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dffba52ff200212d86b7ca97f78c49ba/4b190/2020-07-25-6.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 89.1891891891892%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/dffba52ff200212d86b7ca97f78c49ba/cbe2e/2020-07-25-6.webp 148w,\n/static/dffba52ff200212d86b7ca97f78c49ba/3084c/2020-07-25-6.webp 295w,\n/static/dffba52ff200212d86b7ca97f78c49ba/5ca24/2020-07-25-6.webp 590w,\n/static/dffba52ff200212d86b7ca97f78c49ba/d00b9/2020-07-25-6.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/dffba52ff200212d86b7ca97f78c49ba/a80bd/2020-07-25-6.jpg 148w,\n/static/dffba52ff200212d86b7ca97f78c49ba/1c91a/2020-07-25-6.jpg 295w,\n/static/dffba52ff200212d86b7ca97f78c49ba/1c72d/2020-07-25-6.jpg 590w,\n/static/dffba52ff200212d86b7ca97f78c49ba/4b190/2020-07-25-6.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/dffba52ff200212d86b7ca97f78c49ba/1c72d/2020-07-25-6.jpg\"\n          alt=\"万国图志\"\n          title=\"万国图志\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">万国图志</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>特展：粟特人在大唐</h2>\n<p>这是洛阳博物馆在长沙的特展，就是一堆唐三彩，里面的一个兽面纹还挺像建国的。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/70e788e5ef1634781e84d75da494ef86/4b190/2020-07-25-5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/70e788e5ef1634781e84d75da494ef86/cbe2e/2020-07-25-5.webp 148w,\n/static/70e788e5ef1634781e84d75da494ef86/3084c/2020-07-25-5.webp 295w,\n/static/70e788e5ef1634781e84d75da494ef86/5ca24/2020-07-25-5.webp 590w,\n/static/70e788e5ef1634781e84d75da494ef86/d00b9/2020-07-25-5.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/70e788e5ef1634781e84d75da494ef86/a80bd/2020-07-25-5.jpg 148w,\n/static/70e788e5ef1634781e84d75da494ef86/1c91a/2020-07-25-5.jpg 295w,\n/static/70e788e5ef1634781e84d75da494ef86/1c72d/2020-07-25-5.jpg 590w,\n/static/70e788e5ef1634781e84d75da494ef86/4b190/2020-07-25-5.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/70e788e5ef1634781e84d75da494ef86/1c72d/2020-07-25-5.jpg\"\n          alt=\"唐三彩\"\n          title=\"唐三彩\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">唐三彩</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>","frontmatter":{"category":"travel"},"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/07/25/长沙博物馆还是值得去的.html","date":"July 25, 2020","title":"长沙博物馆还是值得去的"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/travel/2020/07/25/长沙博物馆还是值得去的.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2020/07/24/快速把2D的svg生成为3D.html","title":"快速把2D的svg生成为3D"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/07/26/万家丽真的可以做长沙的硬核代言.html","title":"万家丽真的可以做长沙的硬核代言"},"frontmatter":{"category":"travel"}}}}}